SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?person ) AS ?totalPresidents ) ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?diedInOfficePerson ) AS ?diedInOffice ) ( xsd:decimal ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?diedInOfficePerson ) ) / xsd:decimal ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?person ) ) AS ?proportion ) WHERE {
  {
